import React, { Component } from 'react'; import { Segment, Header } from "semantic-ui-react"; class DataDisplay extends Component { render(){ const { recieveData, currentData } = this.props; const { flightData } = currentData; if(!flightData) return null; return (
Latitude {Math.round(flightData.latitude*100000)/100000 + "º"}
Longitude {Math.round(flightData.longitude*100000)/100000 + "º"}
Relative Direction {Math.round(flightData.direction * 100000) / 100000 + "º"}
Altitude GSP (ft) {Math.round(flightData.altitude*100)/100}
Velocity (m/s) {Math.round(flightData.velocity*100)/100}
TimeElapsed {currentData.timeElapsed}
Payload Prediction (ft) {Math.round(flightData.payloadPredictionDistance * 1000) / 1000 }
CDA Prediction(ft) {Math.round(flightData.CDAPredictionDistance * 1000) / 1000}
); } } export default DataDisplay;
